snippet.textDisplay:
There are many renowned singers who have given their voice to this awesome ghazal. 
If you have listened to the version of Ustad Mehdi Hassab Saab, then this will fall way short. Otherwise, this is definitely one of Atif's finest. Therefore, I go back to Mehdi Hassan's rendition after listening to all others just to have the aftersound of his version lingering in my ear.
